    EToolsDocumentSourceDescriptor

    public static class EToolsDocumentSourceDescriptor.AttributeBuilder
extends RemoteXmlSimpleSearchEngineBaseDescriptor.AttributeBuilder
    Attribute map builder for the EToolsDocumentSource component. You can use this builder as a type-safe alternative to populating the attribute map using attribute keys.

      • site

        public EToolsDocumentSourceDescriptor.AttributeBuilder site(String value)
        Site URL or comma-separated list of site site URLs to which the returned results should be restricted. For example: wikipedia.org or en.wikipedia.org,de.wikipedia.org. Very larger lists of site restrictions (larger than 2000 characters) may result in a processing exception.
